    <p>R Commands Used in this Chapter</p>

    <p>function() - Creates a new function</p>
    <p>return() - Completes a function by returning a value</p>
    <p>tabulate() - Counts occurrences of integer-valued data in a vector</p>
    <p>unique() - Creates a list of unique values in a vector</p>
    <p>match() - Takes two lists and returns values that are in each</p>
    <p>mfv() - Most frequent value (from the modeest package)</p>

  </conclusion>

</chapter>
